ices are best used to measure the price level in a particular month, not to=
 measure price change over time. It is more appropriate to use CPI index va=
lues for the particular item categories to measure price change.<br><br>Pri=
ces, except for electricity, are collected monthly by BLS representatives i=
n the 75 urban areas priced for the CPI. Electricity prices are collected f=
